{"id":59372,"date":"2024-09-25T16:17:29","date_gmt":"2024-09-25T10:47:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=59372"},"modified":"2024-09-27T16:59:56","modified_gmt":"2024-09-27T11:29:56","slug":"kitchen-renovation-cost","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-renovation-cost\/","title":{"rendered":"How Much Does it Cost to Renovate the Kitchen?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Indecisive when it comes to kitchen renovation costs? Explore our blog to decide how to go about it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kitchen renovation costs stumping you every time? We are here to separate the wheat from the chaff!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The terms kitchen renovation and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/before-and-after-kitchen-remodel\/\">kitchen remodelling<\/a> are used interchangeably, but they are different processes. In a kitchen renovation project, the foundational layout and function of the kitchen remain the same, and only the finishes and fixtures are upgraded, while in a kitchen remodelling project, even the foundational features undergo a dramatic change.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For most modern urban homes, homeowners often opt for kitchen renovation rather than remodelling since more cost-effective and versatile options are now available, thanks to technology and knowledge advancement.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what does kitchen renovation actually involve? It involves upgrading or changing the tiles, countertops, storage solutions and wall paint. The final kitchen renovation cost breakdown will be impacted by which elements you plan to change and in which combination PLUS the additional labour cost for kitchen renovation.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162528\/what-does-Kitchen-renovation-involve.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen renovation involves changing tiles, countertops, storage, and paint, affecting overall costs and labour expenses\" class=\"wp-image-59378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162528\/what-does-Kitchen-renovation-involve.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162528\/what-does-Kitchen-renovation-involve-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162528\/what-does-Kitchen-renovation-involve-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162528\/what-does-Kitchen-renovation-involve-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A kitchen island makes the workflow easy <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Final Kitchen Renovation Cost Breakdown: What Influences Your Budget!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Kitchen Cabinets&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>You can change <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-cabinet-design-ideas\/\">kitchen cabinets<\/a> under the countertop or across the walls.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Kitchen cabinets also include drawers, pull-out crockery units, kitchen baskets, decorative knobs, etc.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Consider materials that are mould-resistant and long-lasting, such as solid wood or water-resistant plywood.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Kitchen Tiles<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>You can change the floor or backsplash tiles to give your kitchen a bold, beautiful makeover.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Consider a material that is highly resistant to daily wear and tear and moisture-resistant (Porcelain and quartz are good options).&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Kitchen Appliances &amp; Accessories<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The simplest way to update the kitchen&#8217;s appearance is to replace old appliances with smart gadgets that make cooking quicker and easier. The kitchen can also feature accessories like small artwork or ornate shelves.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Kitchen Countertops<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Determine the length and depth of the kitchen countertop area along the wall to finalise the total cost of the kitchen countertop.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Make use of a mix of semi-precious (quartz) or utilitarian materials (marble or granite) to achieve a balanced look.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Related: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-countertops-options\/\">Best Option For Kitchen Countertops: Take Your Pick Here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Kitchen Wall Paint<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Changing the wall paint is the smallest tweak you can apply to make your kitchen aesthetically beautiful.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A cheaper alternative to wall paint is using a solid colour or subtle-printed wallpapers that mimic the original vibe.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Choose stain-resistant, non-toxic, and odour-resistant wall paint which is easy to wipe down and clean.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Kitchen Electrical Wiring<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Kitchen wiring encompasses all the switchboards, wall plug points, lights and fixtures that you will need to swap out or install in the room during renovation.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162432\/final-kitchen-renovation-cost-breakdown.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen renovation cost breakdown\" class=\"wp-image-59373\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162432\/final-kitchen-renovation-cost-breakdown.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162432\/final-kitchen-renovation-cost-breakdown-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162432\/final-kitchen-renovation-cost-breakdown-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162432\/final-kitchen-renovation-cost-breakdown-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A kitchen countertop with a pull-out tabletop is a blessing<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Renovate Your Kitchen on a Budget?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Replace the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-cabinet-doors\/\">kitchen cabinet doors<\/a> and handles with modified ones to give them a refreshing look and feel.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Install an ultra-modern kitchen countertop (marble or granite) to give your old kitchen a new lease on life.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reset the mood and tone with new lighting options like pendant, recessed, strip, or LED lights.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Integrate stunning <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-backsplash-ideas\/\">kitchen backsplash tiles<\/a> or PVC wallpaper murals to evoke visual interest.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mix up close, ready-to-assemble kitchen cabinets with open wall shelving to balance the kitchen elements.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Consider cork or bamboo kitchen flooring (with a click-lock mechanism and anti-slip properties) for increased safety. You can even paint the floors to keep the budget under control.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Repaint the kitchen cabinets with the right paint (wood paint for wooden cabinets, multipurpose paint for melamine\/laminate) and stain type, or add new moulding or trim if you choose that option.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Repair appliances yourself or with professional help, but don\u2019t completely dispose of them. Ensure safety by only working on appliances that have been fully detached\/unplugged from the water supply.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162457\/how-to-renovate-a-kitchen-on-budget.jpg\" alt=\"How to renovate a kitchen on budget\" class=\"wp-image-59375\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162457\/how-to-renovate-a-kitchen-on-budget.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162457\/how-to-renovate-a-kitchen-on-budget-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162457\/how-to-renovate-a-kitchen-on-budget-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162457\/how-to-renovate-a-kitchen-on-budget-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wall art adds character to the kitchen space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Kitchen Renovation Costs: India, Avoid High Expenditure With Easy Tips<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Don\u2019t have the appetite for high kitchen renovation costs? Check out our easy tips while constructing your kitchen or while renovating through these simple steps:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Build an accessible kitchen by considering a ground-floor plan that places shelves, drawers, and the oven at a convenient height while leaving adequate space for walkways.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Install two kitchen countertops instead of one if you are fond of cooking.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Make your cook space more efficient by locating dishware near the dishwasher, plastic wraps near the workspace for wrapping leftover foods, etc.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pick one focal point in your kitchen design and complement that space with eye-pleasing, lighter and quieter details. At the same time, remember to keep the remaining surfaces simple.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162506\/kitchen-remodelling-tips.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen remodelling tips: Thoughtful layout, dual workspaces, organised storage, and harmonious design details\" class=\"wp-image-59376\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162506\/kitchen-remodelling-tips.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162506\/kitchen-remodelling-tips-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162506\/kitchen-remodelling-tips-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162506\/kitchen-remodelling-tips-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Quirky lighting solves the decor dilemma<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">High-End Kitchen Renovation Cost<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern kitchen costs in India start around Rs. 1,60,000 plus GST. The average cost of kitchen renovation usually depends upon the size of the kitchen and its different elements. Here is a lowdown on the renovation costs for a standard kitchen and a high-end kitchen, respectively.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tip: Add up the costs of the different kitchen elements to reach a final cost for the kitchen renovation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Standard Kitchen Renovation Cost<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Kitchen cabinetry (7 ft. by 9 ft.), including the lofts, will cost around Rs. 3,00,000 to Rs. 4,00,000.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Granite kitchen countertops cost around Rs. 30,000 to Rs. 40,000.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wall Paint costs anywhere between Rs. 8000 to Rs. 10,000<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The cost of procuring high-quality kitchen tiles is between Rs. 15,000 and Rs. 20,000, and the additional cost for installation is Rs. 5000 to Rs. 7000.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">High-End Kitchen Renovation Cost<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>A quartz or caesarstone countertop costs around Rs. 30,000 to Rs. 2,00,000.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wall Paint costs anywhere between Rs. 8000 to Rs. 10,000<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The cost of procuring high-quality kitchen tiles is between Rs. 15,000 and Rs. 20,000, and the additional cost for installation is Rs. 5000 to Rs. 7000.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The renovation cost of a kitchen cabinet (7 ft. by 9 ft.) will be around Rs. 5,00,000 to Rs. 6,00,000, considering the provision of good pantry accessories.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Please note these costs can vary depending on the design, materials, and labour cost.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162445\/high-end-kitchen-renovation-cost.jpg\" alt=\"High-end kitchen renovation costs vary based on design, materials, and labor costs\" class=\"wp-image-59374\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162445\/high-end-kitchen-renovation-cost.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162445\/high-end-kitchen-renovation-cost-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162445\/high-end-kitchen-renovation-cost-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/27162445\/high-end-kitchen-renovation-cost-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add a good quality chimney for a cleaner home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>From a broader perspective, kitchen renovation is quite a thrilling project, but it involves a lot of investment in terms of time and money at various stages of the process. Ensure that you are equipped with all the information beforehand so that you can make an informed decision, especially related to kitchen renovation costs. If you still require any guidance beyond this for your own renovation project, then DesignCafe is there to handhold you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-interior-design-cost\/\">Kitchen Interior Design Costs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-kitchen-design\/\">Modern Kitchen Designs<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>FAQs on Kitchen Remodels<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. What are the types of kitchen remodels?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Minor kitchen remodels<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>It is the simplest and least expensive as it is just a facelift job.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It encompasses re-covering floors, painting walls, replacing lights, buying new appliances, etc.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Partial kitchen remodels<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>It requires more involvement than a basic cosmetic job.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It encompasses installing extra cabinets and countertops, a kitchen island, etc.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Major kitchen remodels<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>It is a complex and expensive kitchen design project.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It encompasses space enlargement, rearrangement of wiring and pipes and improved floor plan.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. How much does a modern kitchen cost &amp; what factors affect it?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The kitchen cabinet material and size<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The brand name and the quality index<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The kitchen accessories and smart appliances<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The versatility in design<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The size and layout of the room<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The external surface finish<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The add-ons to your modern kitchen design, like lighting, island, seating and ventilation mechanisms&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The countertop and backsplash tiling material<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The final cost of a fully functional modern kitchen will be determined by adding up the individual costs of all of the above elements and the additional labour costs for installation.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. What are some of the mistakes that can happen in a kitchen renovation?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Failing to plan properly about the vision and end goal of the renovation project.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Being unrealistic about the budget and its ability to cover your needs completely.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Opting for the wrong flooring can cause accidental slips and other forms of damage.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Installing kitchen cabinets before reworking on the floor as it can expand and contract.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Choosing your smart kitchen appliances after the cabinetry has already been installed.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Forgetting to plan for extra storage space for unforeseen deliveries.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ignoring the kitchen triangle between the sink, refrigerator and stove hampering work efficiency.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Conducting incomplete research about kitchen elements and rushing to make the final decision.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"lef